<treatmentCitation id="027B10FCFFB6FF9764BAFC3DFE49FC56" author="REITTER E." box="[151,408,994,1013]" page="151" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" year="1916">
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF9764BAFC3DFE49FC56" authority="Reitter, 1916: 151" authorityName="Reitter" authorityPageNumber="151" authorityYear="1916" box="[151,408,994,1013]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Tagenostola" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF9764BAFC3DFF2FFC56" box="[151,254,994,1013]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Tagenostola</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF97652FFC3DFE49FC56" author="REITTER E." box="[258,408,994,1013]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="129 - 171" refId="ref13173" refString="REITTER E. 1916: Bestimmungstabelle der Tenebrioniden, enthaltend die Zopherini, Elenophorini, Leptodini, Stenosini und Lachnogyini aus der palaarktischen Fauna. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 35: 129 - 171." type="journal article" year="1916">Reitter, 1916:151</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</treatmentCitation>
(original description). 
<typeStatus id="5C61884FFFB6FF97667AFC3DFD50FC56" box="[599,641,994,1013]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Type</typeStatus>
species: 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF9766E1FC3DFC21FC56" authority="Reitter, 1886" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1886" box="[716,1008,994,1013]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Stenosis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="turkestanica">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF9766E1FC3DFCAFFC56" box="[716,894,994,1013]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Stenosis turkestanica</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF9767AFFC3DFC21FC56" author="REITTER E." box="[898,1008,994,1013]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="7 - 144" refId="ref13149" refString="REITTER E. 1886: Revision der mit Stenosis verwandten Coleopteren der alten Welt. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 30: 7 - 144." type="journal article" year="1886">Reitter, 1886</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, subsequently designatated by 
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF97656DFC22FE6DFBB3" author="GEBIEN H." box="[320,444,1021,1040]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="505 - 883" refId="ref12717" refString="GEBIEN H. 1937: Katalog der Tenebrioniden (Col. Heteromera) Teil I. Pubblicazioni del Museo Entomologico ' Pietro Rossi' 2: 505 - 883." type="journal article" year="1937">GEBIEN (1937)</bibRefCitation>
.
</treatmentCitationGroup>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFB6FF9764BAFBF7FB95FB3C" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFB6FF9764BAFBF7FB95FB3C" blockId="6.[151,1127,1064,1343]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF9764BAFBF7FEDDFB9C" bold="true" box="[151,268,1064,1087]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF9765A9FBF7FDD4FB9C" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1916" box="[388,517,1064,1087]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Tagenostola" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF9765A9FBF7FDD4FB9C" box="[388,517,1064,1087]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Tagenostola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is characterized by eyes not divided into upper and lower parts by genae; eyes in lateral view not diminished to narrow transverse band of facets in lower part; pronotum longer than wide and distinctly narrower than head; tempora almost straightly narrowed to cervical constriction; elytra are on humeral part suddenly narrowed to base.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="CBC06566FFB6FF9764BAFB77FCDFFA9C" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="836536EDFFB6FF9764BAFB77FCDFFA9C" blockId="6.[151,1127,1064,1343]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF9764BAFB77FED7FB1C" bold="true" box="[151,262,1192,1215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF976520FB77FDC4FB1C" author="ARNDT E. &amp; FERRER J." box="[269,533,1192,1215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="253 - 255" refId="ref12522" refString="ARNDT E. &amp; FERRER J. 1997: Remarks on the genus Tagenostola Reitter (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae). Koleopterologische Rundschau 67: 253 - 255." type="journal article" year="1997">ARNDT &amp; FERRER (1997)</bibRefCitation>
stated that the 
<typeStatus id="5C61884FFFB6FF976692FB77FD3CFB1C" box="[703,749,1192,1215]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">type</typeStatus>
species is 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF97674BFB77FF07FB7C" authority="(Reitter, 1886)" baseAuthorityName="Reitter" baseAuthorityYear="1886" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Stenosis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="turkestanica">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF97674BFB77FBD6FB1C" box="[870,1031,1192,1215]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">T. turkestanica</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF97603AFB77FF1FFB7C" author="REITTER E." pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="7 - 144" refId="ref13149" refString="REITTER E. 1886: Revision der mit Stenosis verwandten Coleopteren der alten Welt. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift 30: 7 - 144." type="journal article" year="1886">Reitter, 1886</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
by ‘original description’. However, 
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF976675FB17FD29FB7C" author="REITTER E." box="[600,760,1224,1247]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="129 - 171" refId="ref13173" refString="REITTER E. 1916: Bestimmungstabelle der Tenebrioniden, enthaltend die Zopherini, Elenophorini, Leptodini, Stenosini und Lachnogyini aus der palaarktischen Fauna. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 35: 129 - 171." type="journal article" year="1916">REITTER (1916)</bibRefCitation>
did not designate any 
<typeStatus id="5C61884FFFB6FF9767C8FB17FBC2FB7C" box="[997,1043,1224,1247]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">type</typeStatus>
species for 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF976490FB37FEEFFB5C" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1916" box="[189,318,1256,1279]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Tagenostola" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF976490FB37FEEFFB5C" box="[189,318,1256,1279]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">Tagenostola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but just included 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF976629FB37FD73FB5C" baseAuthorityName="Reitter" baseAuthorityYear="1886" box="[516,674,1256,1279]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Stenosis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="turkestanica">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF976629FB37FD73FB5C" box="[516,674,1256,1279]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">T. turkestanica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF9766F8FB37FC09FB5C" authority="Reitter, 1916" authorityName="Reitter" authorityYear="1916" box="[725,984,1256,1279]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Tagenostola" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="muelleri">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF9766F8FB37FC99FB5C" box="[725,840,1256,1279]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">T. muelleri</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF976762FB37FC09FB5C" author="REITTER E." box="[847,984,1256,1279]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="129 - 171" refId="ref13173" refString="REITTER E. 1916: Bestimmungstabelle der Tenebrioniden, enthaltend die Zopherini, Elenophorini, Leptodini, Stenosini und Lachnogyini aus der palaarktischen Fauna. Wiener Entomologische Zeitung 35: 129 - 171." type="journal article" year="1916">
Reitter, 
<quantity id="44229B08FFB6FF97678EFB37FC09FB5C" box="[931,984,1256,1279]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.86664" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" unit="in" value="1916.0">1916</quantity>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
in the genus. Subsequently 
<bibRefCitation id="E74B4B1CFFB6FF976503FAD7FE17FABC" author="GEBIEN H." box="[302,454,1288,1311]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" pagination="505 - 883" refId="ref12717" refString="GEBIEN H. 1937: Katalog der Tenebrioniden (Col. Heteromera) Teil I. Pubblicazioni del Museo Entomologico ' Pietro Rossi' 2: 505 - 883." type="journal article" year="1937">GEBIEN (1937)</bibRefCitation>
stated that the 
<typeStatus id="5C61884FFFB6FF97664AFAD7FD44FABC" box="[615,661,1288,1311]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">type</typeStatus>
species is 
<taxonomicName id="44DA4D6EFFB6FF976725FAD7FC77FABC" baseAuthorityName="Reitter" baseAuthorityYear="1886" box="[776,934,1288,1311]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" genus="Stenosis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="223" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="turkestanica">
<emphasis id="B1AEEAFFFFB6FF976725FAD7FC77FABC" box="[776,934,1288,1311]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">T. turkestanica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which the author of the present paper considers the 
<typeStatus id="5C61884FFFB6FF976629FAF7FDE3FA9C" box="[516,562,1320,1343]" pageId="6" pageNumber="223">type</typeStatus>
species designation.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
